# NetPeek curated probes (starter)
Probe TCP NULL q||
rarity 0

Probe TCP GetRequest q|GET / HTTP/1.0\r\n\r\n|
ports 80,443,8080,8443
rarity 1

Probe TCP SshHello q|\r\n|
ports 22
rarity 1

Probe TCP MysqlHello q|\x00|
ports 3306
rarity 2

match http m|^HTTP/1\.[01] ([0-9]{3})|s
softmatch http m|^HTTP/|s
match ssh m|^SSH-([0-9]+\.[0-9]+)-([^\r\n]+)|
match mysql m|mysql|i
softmatch ssl m|^\x16\x03|s
